
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>CodeAmide - Application Submitted</title>
    <style>  
    body {
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: #333;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
}

header {
    background-color: #333;
    padding: 1rem;
}

header h1 {
    color: #fff;
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin: 0;
}

main {
    max-width: 500px;
    margin: 2rem auto;
    padding: 1rem;
    background-color: #f4f4f4;
    border: 1px solid #ddd;
    border-radius: 4px;
    text-align: center;
}

main h1 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 0;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    border-bottom:2px solid #333;
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
}

main p {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

.button {
    display: inline-block;
    background-color: #333;
    color: #fff;
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 4px;
    text-decoration: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
}

.button:hover {
    background-color: #444;
}

footer {
    background-color: #333;
    padding: 1rem;
    text-align: center;
    color: #fff;
    margin-top: 2rem;
}
</style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>CodeAmide</h1>
    </header>
    <main>
        <h1>Application Submitted</h1>
        <p>Please save this ID for future reference:</p>
        <p>Application ID: <%= apply_id %></p>
        <a href="/codeamide/about" class="button">Back to Home</a>
    </main>
    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2023 CodeAmide</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>